wikipedia_page.main: Peter Millar is a retired Scottish-American soccer forward.  He spent nine seasons in the second American Soccer League, one in the North American Soccer League and four in the German American Soccer League.  He also earned thirteen caps, scoring eight goals, with the U.S. national team between 1968 and 1972.
